						<p>Pāṇḍya, Jaṭāvarman Kulaśēkhara, 13+5th year = A.D. 1208.</p>						

						<p>A <hi rend="italic">kaikkōḷa</hi> resident of the temple street gave the jamb stone for the entrance into the <hi rend="italic">ardha-maṇḍapa</hi> of the temple of Kuṟaḷmāṇīśvaram-udāiyār at Iḍattuvaḷi in Cheṅgāṭṭirukkai in Veṇbil-nāḍu.</p>						

						<p>[Published in <hi rend="italic">Virudhunagar District Inscriptions</hi>, No. 133/2005.]</p>						

