<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi> kOccaṭaipaṉmarāṉa tiripuvaṉac cakkaravattika
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ḷ <hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi>kulacēkaratēvaṟku yāṇṭu <num value="13"><g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num> Etir 5 cāvatu veṇpilnā
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṭṭuc ceṅkāṭṭirukkai Iṭattuvaḷi nāyaṉāṟ kuṟaḷ māṇī
<lb n="4" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">śva</hi>muṭaiya nāyaṉār tirumaṭaiviḷākattil kaikkOḷaril
<lb n="5"/>kuḻaiñcāṉ caṅkaṉāṉa puravari mārāyaṉ ṉāyaṉār kōyilaṟtta
<lb n="6"/>maṇṭapattil tiruvāyal tiruṉilaikāl ṉaṭṭivittāṉ Itu Iva
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṉ taṉmam <hi rend="grantha">svastiśrī</hi>
</p>

